at may change this Privacy Policy at any time by publishing the new version on the app.\r\n\r\n**Verifying, updating and amending personal information Presto Eat**\r\nYou can update your personal information at any time by logging-in to your account and\r\naccessing your profile, where you can update your personal information mentioned.`, // your Markdown content
